elements.description: # Welcome to Ocean Innovate: Pioneering Regeneration Seaworthy Welcome to **Ocean Innovate**, a community dedicated to pioneering solutions for ocean regeneration. Our mission is to harness the power of technology, innovation, and collaboration to address the critical challenges facing our oceans. We believe that by working together, we can restore the health and vitality of marine ecosystems around the globe. ## Our Mission and Vision At **Ocean Innovate**, our vision is a world where the oceans are thriving, resilient, and abundant. We are committed to creating and supporting innovative technologies that can lead to significant, positive changes in ocean health. From combating pollution to promoting sustainable fishing practices, our community is at the forefront of the ocean regeneration movement. ## Why the Ocean Matters The ocean is the heart of our planet, regulating climate, providing food, and supporting a vast biodiversity. However, human activities have put our oceans at risk. Pollution, overfishing, and climate change are just a few of the challenges that threaten marine life and, by extension, human life. At **Ocean Innovate**, we understand the urgency of these issues and are dedicated to making a difference. ## Join Our Community We invite startups, researchers, environmentalists, and technology enthusiasts to join us in our mission. Whether you are working on a new ocean tech innovation or are passionate about marine conservation, **Ocean Innovate** offers a platform to connect, share ideas, and collaborate on projects that can lead to real-world impact. Together, we can work towards regenerating our oceans and ensuring a sustainable future for all. Learn more about our Needs mapping here Be a part of our journey. Join **Ocean Innovate** today and help us turn the tide on ocean health. Let's innovate for the oceans, for our planet, and for future generations.

### Resources from Rethinking Economics at the Design School for Regenerating Earth



* Video: [Why Gift Giving Makes No Sense (Adam Ruins Everyting)](https://design-school-for-regenerating-earth.mn.co/posts/rethinking-economics-why-gift-giving-makes-no-sense-adam-ruins-everything-45928322)
* Article: [Liminal Economics: Swimming at the Edge of the Economy](https://medium.com/onioncollective/liminal-economics-swimming-at-the-edge-of-the-economy-f16fb476daa4) 
* Article: [Doughnut Economics](https://www.kateraworth.com/doughnut/)
* Video: [REA Accounting](https://youtu.be/WCG_MrKOLi4)
* Video: [Common Welfare Economy](https://youtu.be/D3Z2cXK5mhc)
* Article: [What is the Reputation Economy?](https://medium.com/sacred-capital/how-does-the-reputation-economy-work-60bf8c43a84b)
* Article: [Dimensions of Incentives](https://www.artbrock.com/targeted-currencies/vision)
* Article: [The Buy Nothing Movement](https://buynothingproject.org/)
* Video: [Gift Economies](https://www.ted.com/talks/alex_gendler_what_is_a_gift_economy)
* Article: [Types of Commons Economies](https://centerforneweconomics.org/apply/the-commons-program/movement/)
* Article: [Accounting for Planetary Survival](https://p2pfoundation.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/AccountingForPlanetarySurvival_def.pdf), _Michel Bauwens and Alex Pazaitis_
* Website: [Peer to Peer Foundation](https://p2pfoundation.net/)
* Article: [A Society Without Money](https://www.capitalismmagazine.com/2022/01/is-a-society-without-money-possible-or-desirable/), _Thomas Walker-Werth_

* Article:_ _[Gameshifting for effective meetings](https://www.artbrock.com/2014/11/08/gameshifting-tools-for-group-self-facilitation), _Arthur Brock_

* Video: [Village Network Simulation](https://www.gaia.com/article/world-without-money), _Will Ruddick_
